snippet: The Florida men took home their first outdoor national and the Louisiana State women won their 15th in 31 years at the N.C.A.A. track and field meet in Des Moines.
abstract: Florida men home their first outdoor national track and field title and the Louisiana State women win their 15th in 31 years at the NCAA track and field meet in Des Moines; other track news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Florida men took home their first outdoor national and the Louisiana State women won their 15th in 31 years at the N.C.A.A. track and field meet in Des Moines.
